# Tasks — {{PROJECT_NAME}}

Active work only — status `in progress` or `in review`. This file should stay short by construction: not-yet-started ideas live in `BACKLOG.md` instead, and a task moves out to `TASKS_ARCHIVE.md` the instant it reaches `done` (not at session end). If this file is getting long, either too much is being worked in parallel, or `done` tasks aren't being archived promptly — either way, worth noticing.

One entry per task, in the format below. Status values in this file: `backlog` (transiently, right when `scope` creates the entry, before the blueprint is approved), `in progress`, `in review`.

